# Hover & Interaction

Hover-only effects (e.g. link raise, button highlight) must be wrapped in a media query so they never fire on touch screens:

```css
@media (hover: hover) and (pointer: fine) {
    .my-element:hover {
        /* hover styles */
    }
}
```
